Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:41.58,kaci,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,180)\fad(200,200)}就连这种人之常情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:47.79,kasi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(40,180)\fad(200,200)}この手で切り裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:47.79,kaci,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,180)\fad(200,200)}我也要将其亲手斩断
